title: Hollow Wood - Wallflower EP (2015)
description:
With roots in earnest and truthful music, Hollow Wood maintains a balance of intimacy and power that blend together to create an incredibly engaging musical experience. Formed in Boise, Idaho in 2010, Hollow Wood consists of an organic and consistently evolving lineup of musicians who are devoted to expressing music in an honest way. Morgan Schuler of KEXP in Seattle writes, â€œEven now, I can remember being wrapped up in it as the crowd cheered, danced and clapped their way through the set.â€
